name: Outstanding Invoices by Date
query:
select 
name "ID:Link/Sales Invoice:100",
posting_date "Date:Date:100",
customer "Customer:Link/Customer:200",
payment_terms_template "Payment Terms:Data:100",
grand_total "Total:Currency:100",
paid_amount "Paid:Currency:100",
outstanding_amount  "Outstanding:Currency:100",
company "Company:Link/Company:200"

from `tabSales Invoice` 

where 
grand_total-1>paid_amount
and outstanding_amount >0
and docstatus=1
and posting_date >= %(fdate)s
and posting_date <= %(tdate)s
order by customer
